Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Pratt Real Estate Development in conjunction with its partners have developed a preeminent retail portfolio in the heart of Altoona Iowa.  The project is anchored by a 4 story mixed use apartment and retail building.  The building is not only the tallest property in Altoona but commands the highest rents in the apartment market as well.  The first floor retail consist of retail/office and services providers.  The development is adjacent to the Altoona Hy-Vee Grocery store and the Prairie Heritage Civic Plaza and close to the Altoona YMCA.  This location gives residents and tenants a true live/work/play walkable environment that is rare outside of the CBD.  Further the development was designed with common shared and street parking concept to accommodate not only residents and commercial tenants, but customers from outside the area as well.  This design creates adequate parking for all and walkability.
